         <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="Section_H">
            
            
            <xs:annotation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed Heat Pump System - Efficiency and Performance Compliance Information</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">In this section parent CC refers to the parent CF1R Certificate of Compliance (CC)
 
 This Section is applicable only if at least one system in section C has C04_ResidentialHeatingSystemType  Or C05_ResidentialCoolingSystemType == CentralLargePackagedHP, CentralPackagedHP, CentralSplitHP,  DuctlessSplitHP (display term Ductless mini-split HP), DuctedMiniSplitHP, AirToWaterHeatPump, GroundSourceHeatPump,  DuctedMultiSplitHP, DuctlessMultiSplitHP, DuctedDuctlessMultiSplitHP, DuctlessVRF_HP, SmallDuctHighVelocityHP, HydronicHP, HydronicHP_ForcedAir, RoomHP, VCHP_IndoorUnitDucted, VCHP_IndoorUnitDuctless or VCHP_IndoorUnitDuctedAndDuctless, SPVHP, PTHP.    Require one row of data in this table for each of the SC Systems for which the system type  is in this list.</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="MinOccurs">If this section doesn't apply, display only the section FieldText and the statement 'This section does not apply to this project.'</xs:documentation>
               
            
            </xs:annotation>
            
            
            <xs:complexType>
               
               
               <xs:sequence>
                  
                  
                  <xs:element name="TableHeatPumpPerf">
                     
                     
                     <xs:annotation>
                        
                        
