                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If B06_EfficiencyType IsPresent As 
default result = B06_EfficiencyType and Allow user to override default and select from list: EER, EER2, EERSEER, EER2SEER2, CEER;  Flag non-default values and report in project status notes field; a revised parent CC may be required.
Else user selects from list:  EER, EER2, SEER, SEER2, EERSEER, EER2SEER2, CEER</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
