 If B07_NotApplicableMessage IsPresent  
If E03_EfficiencyType == SEER or EERSEER Then 
If result GTE 14 result complies
Else result does not comply
End If
End If
Else If B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueSEER IsPresent
If result  GTE B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueSEER, 
result complies
Else result does not comply
End If
End If
 
Flag non-compliant values and do not let registration proceed if not in compliance.</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
