 If B07_NotApplicableMessage IsPresent Then If E03_EfficiencyType == SEER2 or EER2SEER2 Then If result GTE 13.4 result complies Elseif H07 = CEER, then value = N/A Else result does not comply End If End If
Else If B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueSEER2 IsPresent Then If result  GTE B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueSEER2, result complies Else result does not comply End If End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
