                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">User input EER2 numeric xx.x within InclusiveRange(0.0, 100.0).   Check result: 
 If B07_NotApplicableMessage IsPresent Then If E03_EfficiencyType == EER2 or EER2SEER2 Then If result GTE 11.2 result complies Else result does not comply End If End If
Else If B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueEER2 IsPresent If result  GTE B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueEER2, result complies Else result does not comply End If End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
