                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">User input CEER numeric xx.x within InclusiveRange(0.0, 100.0).   Check result: If result  GTE B07_EfficiencyMinimumValueCEER, result complies;  Flag non-compliant values and do not allow registration to proceed if not in compliance.</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
